name: classic beauty
description: i really enjoyed doing this piece. i love playing with my art style bit by bit so i can create something a little bit different every time!! which also means my art style is uh... inconsistent sometimes, but thats okay!! i really like how peaceful and graceful this drawing is, which is so polar opposite from me sometimes, that it kind of helps me come to an ease looking at it. i hope it gives you the same feeling!
